ra takes care of lunch for all the people working on the farm. She is such a sweet lady and definitely knows how to make mouth-watering meals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4123&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142805\/bali-stay-with-locals-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142805\/bali-stay-with-locals-pin-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142805\/bali-stay-with-locals-pin-375x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Homestay Bali: Experience local life of Bali, Indonesia\" height=\"600\" width=\"375\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Most of the meals were prepared with fresh ingredients from their own farm. You can learn about the ingredients used or ask if you can cook together with Era.<br><br><strong>Oh and; <\/strong>The local sweet snacks were incredible by the way!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"bali stay with locals snack\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bali stay with locals snack\" data-id=\"11665\" data-link=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/travel-blogs\/staying-with-locals-bali\/attachment\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack\/\" class=\"wp-image-11665 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142906\/bali-stay-with-locals-snack-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads